  "title": "Primary School Health Screening  #HMS",
  "description": "<p>Primary School Health Screening </p><p>We are looking for Locum Admin staff to support school health screening in Primary Schools.</p><p> Location: Mainly Central & North</p><p> Pay: $10/hr ( no CPF)</p><p> Commitment: Minimum 6 months</p><p> Workdays: 4–5 days/week</p><p> Working Hours:</p><p>Mon–Fri, 7.30am – 4.00pm</p><p> Job Scope / Training Objective</p><p>Height & weight measurement</p><p>Snellen test (eye check)</p><p>Audiometry test (hearing)</p><p> Requirements</p><p>Vaccinated for:</p><p>MMR (if born before Jan 1974, not required)</p><p>Tdap (valid within last 10 years)</p><p>IT-savvy candidates preferred</p><p> Training (Not Paid)</p><p>For candidates who have not attended HPB training:</p><p>Training Dates:</p><p>1st session: 4 Feb, 3.30pm – 5.30pm</p><p>Total 3 training sessions (must complete all)</p><p>Can start work after 1st training, but must continue and complete 2nd & 3rd sessions</p><p>Training Venue:  @ Ubi</p><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan </p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
